lead_paragraph: Fredy Montero snatched a late winner as Portuguese league leaders Sporting came from behind to beat Academica Coimbra 3-2 on Saturday, despite having coach Jorge Jesus sent off.

headline.print_headline: Sporting Snatch Dramatic Win to Stay Top in Portugal
headline.main: Sporting Snatch Dramatic Win to Stay Top in Portugal
